metadata.name: Coversation I — For All The Doubts and Smiles
metadata.description:
At first, I don’t have anything particular in mind about this artwork. I was just drawing the 2 characters both facing each others upside downs. Until my good old friend Abraham asked me “Is that us?” Then it occurred to me that it truly is an illustration of what I’ve been doing lately with him. We had a lot of conversation together, bouncing ideas here and there like a tennis match. And also shared a lot of our restlessness and wishes together. 

Conversations will be continued…
